<p style="text-align: justify;">The family of both stars are very supportive and spend a quality time with them and help when they were busy. Bradley Cooper is preparing for his next movie on following year <strong><em>A Star Is Born</em></strong> and this will be his debut directorial venture and Irina is focusing on her career and her physique is even toned than earlier. She spends a lot of time in the gym for a nonstop workout.</p>
