<p style="text-align: justify;">Cristiano Ronaldo ex-girlfriend Irina hit Cannes Film Festival wearing a yellow gown, showing off her incredible figure. Bradley Cooper may be busy with their daughter in the home or may be in the filming. Irina, 31 and Cooper, 42 have been in a relationship since 2015 after she split with Real Madrid superstar Cristiano Ronaldo.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Cooper is also busy with the release of most anticipated Marvel film ‚Äú<strong>Avengers: Infinity War</strong>‚Äù which is slated to be released in 2018.The Oscar-nominated actor will play the voice over the character of Rocket Raccoon in Anthony Russo and Joe Russo directorial venture according to the sources.</p>
